「GTA」一詞首見於一份在1980年代中期就區内地方行政架構重組問題而發表的報告中，其後才開始被廣泛使用，並被省政府定為一個正式的規劃範圍。雖然[[哈密爾頓_(安大略省)|咸美頓市]]與多倫多市及其近郊城鎮關係密切，但大多倫多地區公認的覆蓋範圍多年來一直沒有包括該市。然而，隨著城市帶不斷發展，大多地區和咸美頓市從2000年代起在區域規劃和公共政策等範疇内被一併研究，多個政府機構亦開始使用'''大多倫多暨咸美頓地區'''（Greater Toronto and Hamilton Area，簡稱GTHA）{{ref|GTHA|a}}一詞來表達大多倫多地區和咸美頓市（包括前{{le|溫特沃斯縣|Wentworth County, Ontario}}）所覆蓋的範圍；此區域於2008年約有6,539,700名居民。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fin.gov.on.ca/en/economy/demographics/projections/table6.html |title=存档副本 |language=en |accessdate=2010-06-04 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117133638/https://www.fin.gov.on.ca/en/economy/demographics/projections/table6.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>「GTHA」一詞目前尚未被民眾廣泛使用。

另外，「[[金馬蹄地區|大金馬蹄地區]]」（Greater Golden Horseshoe）從2006年起亦開始應用在地方規劃的範疇中<ref name="MIERE">{{cite web|url = http://www.mei.gov.on.ca/en/pdf/infrastructure/GrowthPlan_Brochure.pdf|title = Planning for Growth|work = Understanding the Growth Plan for the Greater Golden Horseshoe|language = en|publisher = Ministry of Public Infrastructure Renewal|date = |deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110706192438/http://www.mei.gov.on.ca/en/pdf/infrastructure/GrowthPlan_Brochure.pdf|archivedate = 2011-07-06|accessdate = 2010-06-04}}</ref>；此詞亦涵蓋[[巴里_(安大略省)|巴里]]市、[[貴湖|貴湖]]市和[[尼亞加拉區|尼亞加拉區]]等地。然而，安省政府其它部門（如[[安大略省財政廳|安大略省財政廳]]）仍然使用「GTA」一詞。

==歷史==
[[Image:YorkCountyOntario1880s.jpg|thumb]]
在歐洲人抵達現大多倫多地區前，該帶是多個[[加拿大原住民|原住民族]]的聚居地：{{le|中立原住民族|Neutral Nation}}<ref>{{cite book |title=The Archaeology Of Southern Ontario To A.D. 1650 |editors= Chris J. Ellis & Neal Ferris |language=en |year=1990 |publisher=London Chapter of the Ontario Archaeological Society|isbn=0-919350-13-5 |pages=410–411}}</ref>、{{le|塞尼卡族|Seneca nation}}、{{le|莫霍克族|Mohawk nation}}和{{le|休倫族|Wyandot}}曾於不同年代定居於此。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.toronto.ca/culture/history/history-first-peoples.htm|title = First Peoples, 9000 BCE to 1600 CE|work = Toronto Culture – Exploring Toronto's past|language = en|publisher = City of Toronto|date = |accessdate = 2010-06-04|archive-date = 2011-06-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110606115751/http://www.toronto.ca/culture/history/history-first-peoples.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>{{le|密西沙加族|Mississaugas}}則於17世紀末和18世紀初抵達該帶，並趕走原居於此的[[易洛魁聯盟|易洛魁人]]。<ref>''The Ojibwa-Iroquois War: The War the Five Nations Did Not Win''. Leroy V. Eid. Ethnohistory, Vol. 26, No. 4 (Autumn, 1979), Duke University Press,pp. 297-324 {{language icon|en}}</ref><ref>Schmalz, Peter S., ''The Ojibwa of Southern Ontario.'' University of Toronto Press. ISBN 0-8020-2736-9. pp 21-22 {{language icon|en}}</ref>歐洲人亦於17世紀抵達現多倫多一帶。<ref name = "PRE1930XIV">{{cite web|url = http://www.toronto.ca/culture/history/history-natives-newcomers.htm|title = Natives and Newcomers, 1600-1793|work = Toronto Culture – Exploring Toronto's past|language = en|publisher = City of Toronto|year = 2009|accessdate = 2010-06-04|archive-date = 2007-03-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070306111515/http://www.toronto.ca/culture/history/history-natives-newcomers.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>

連接[[安大略湖|安大略湖]]、[[錫姆科湖|錫姆科湖]]和[[大湖區|大湖區]]上游處的一條水陸聯運路線由此而過，叫做{{le|多倫多運輸線|Toronto Carrying-Place Trail}}，<ref>{{cite web|title=The Toronto Carrying-place|url=http://www.natureconservancy.ca/site/News2?page=NewsArticle&id=5666&news_iv_ctrl=0&abbr=on_ncc_|publisher=Nature Conservancy of Canada|accessdate=2010-02-28|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100619065456/http://www.natureconservancy.ca/site/News2?page=NewsArticle&id=5666&news_iv_ctrl=0&abbr=on_ncc_|archivedate=2010-06-19}}</ref>令此處成為法裔皮草商人進行交易的要點。<ref name = "PRE1930XIV" />[[法國|法國]]於1720年代在此處建立{{le|皇家倉庫|Magasin Royale}}（於數年間被遺棄），再於1750年代建立一個{{le|要塞|Fort Rouillé}}，卻於[[七年戰爭|七年戰爭]]期間被英軍毀掉，<ref name="PRE1930XIV"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://geonames.nrcan.gc.ca/education/toronto_e.php |title=The real story of how Toronto got its name |work=Mapping Services |author=Rayburn, Alan |publisher=Natural Resources Canada |date=2007-09-18 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111209114921/http://geonames.nrcan.gc.ca/education/toronto_e.php |archivedate=2011-12-09 |accessdate=2010-06-04 }}</ref>戰爭過後此處亦歸[[英國|英國]]所有。

[[美國獨立戰爭|美國獨立戰爭]]過後，大批忠於英國的[[十三州殖民地|十三州殖民地]]居民遷居此處，為現大多倫多地區帶來第一波歐洲裔移民潮。<ref name = "PRE1930XIV" />英國政府於1787年從{{le|密西沙加族|Mississaugas of the New Credit First Nation}}購入超過25萬英畝（1000平方公里）的土地，史稱{{le|多倫多購地|Toronto Purchase}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.newcreditfirstnation.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=19&Itemid=28 |title=Missisaugas of the New Credit CURRENT LAND CLAIMS |language=en |accessdate=2010-06-04 |archive-date=2011-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714172625/http://www.newcreditfirstnation.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=19&Itemid=28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{le|约克县 (安大略省)|York County, Ontario|约克县}}隨後於1792年成立，範圍一度覆蓋現多倫多市、荷頓區、皮爾區、約克區、以及杜林區小部分地區。<ref>{{cite web |title=Ontario's Districts - 1798 |url=http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/english/on-line-exhibits/maps/textdocs/districts1798big.aspx |publisher=Queen's Printer |accessdate=2010-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110212153904/http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/english/on-line-exhibits/maps/textdocs/districts1798big.aspx |language=en |archivedate=2011-02-12 |dead-url=yes |location=Ontario }}</ref>{{le|約克鎮|York, Upper Canada}}（現多倫多市）於[[1812年戰爭|1812年戰爭]]中被美軍破壞。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.toronto.ca/culture/history/history-provincial-centre.htm|title=A Provincial Centre, 1793-1851|work=Toronto Culture – Exploring Toronto's past|author=|publisher=City of Toronto|year=2009|language=en|accessdate=2010-06-04|archive-date=2011-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607104503/http://www.toronto.ca/culture/history/history-provincial-centre.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

溫特沃斯縣和荷頓縣於1816年脫離約克縣，自組地方行政架構。<ref name="ARONT">{{cite web|url=http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/english/on-line-exhibits/maps/ontario-county-table.aspx|title=18th and 19th Century Ontario Counties and Corresponding Districts|work=|author=Archives of Ontario|language=en|publisher=Queen's Printer, Ontario|date=2010-02-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100213030102/http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/english/on-line-exhibits/maps/ontario-county-table.aspx|archivedate=2010-02-13|accessdate=2010-06-04}}</ref>{{le|上加拿大叛亂|Upper Canada Rebellion}}其後在約克縣爆發，由[[威廉·萊昂·麥肯齊|威廉·萊昂·麥肯齊]]帶領民眾反抗英國殖民政府。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://edrh.rhpl.richmondhill.on.ca/default.asp?ID=s5.4|title = The Road to Rebellion|work = Tories and Reformers|author = Robert M. Stamp|publisher = Town of Richmond Hill Public Library|year = 1991|language = en|accessdate = 2010-06-04|archive-date = 2011-09-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110928222942/http://edrh.rhpl.richmondhill.on.ca/default.asp?ID=s5.4|dead-url = no}}</ref>安大略縣和皮爾縣於1851年脫離約克縣，<ref name=ARONT /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/english/on-line-exhibits/maps/textdocs/ontario-districts-1851.aspx|title=Ontario's Districts - 1851|language=en|work=The Evolution of the District and County System 1788-1899|author=Archives of Ontario|publisher=Queen's Printer, Ontario|date=2010-02-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611063147/http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/english/on-line-exhibits/maps/textdocs/ontario-districts-1851.aspx|archivedate=2011-06-11|accessdate=2010-06-04}}</ref>而約克縣位於[[士刁士大道|士刁士大道]]以南的地段（即多倫多市及其内圈近郊城鎮）則於1953年脫離約克縣，並改組成[[大多倫多市|大多倫多市]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=Municipality of Metropolitan Toronto Act |url=http://www.e-laws.gov.on.ca/html/repealedstatutes/english/elaws_rep_statutes_90m62_e.htm |language=en |publisher=Queen's Printer |accessdate=2010-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110105121125/http://www.e-laws.gov.on.ca/html/repealedstatutes/english/elaws_rep_statutes_90m62_e.htm |archivedate=2011-01-05 |dead-url=no |location=Ontario }}</ref>大多倫多市成立後，約克縣的縣治從多倫多遷往[[紐馬克特_(安大略省)|紐馬克]]。大多倫多市政府亦有權操控鄰近城鎮（如[[旺市|旺市]]、[[萬錦|萬錦]]和皮克靈等）的規劃事務，但那些城市卻不在大多市的正式管轄範圍以内。

大多市原先由{{le|舊多倫多市|Toronto (former)}}、五個鄉（{{le|東約克|East York}}、[[怡陶碧谷|怡陶碧谷]]、[[北約克|北約克]]、[[士嘉堡|士嘉堡]]和{{le|约克 (多伦多)|York, Toronto}}）以及另外七個村和鎮組成；那七個村鎮於1967年併入舊多倫多市和上列五鄉。<ref name=AROMY />約克縣的餘下部分則於1971年改組成[[約克區|約克區]]。<ref name="AROMY">{{cite web|url=http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/english/on-line-exhibits/maps/counties/rm-york.aspx|title=Municipality of Metropolitan Toronto and the Regional Municipality of York|language=en|author=Archives of Ontario|publisher=Queen's Printer, Ontario|date=2010-02-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090619072740/http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/english/on-line-exhibits/maps/counties/rm-york.aspx|archivedate=2009-06-19|accessdate=2010-06-04}}</ref> 北約克、約克、怡陶碧谷和士嘉堡於1980年代先後改設市，而此四市聯同舊多倫多市、東約克和大多市的行政架構於{{le|1998年多伦多合并|Amalgamation of Toronto#1998 Amalgamation|1998年合併}}成新的多倫多市。<ref>{{cite web |title=City of Toronto Act, 1997 |url=http://www.canlii.org/en/on/laws/stat/so-1997-c-2/latest/so-1997-c-2.html |language=en |publisher=Queen's Printer |accessdate=2010-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017200518/http://www.canlii.org/en/on/laws/stat/so-1997-c-2/latest/so-1997-c-2.html |archivedate=2015-10-17 |dead-url=no |location=Ontario }}</ref>

==多倫多人口普查都會區==
[[File:Toronto_Location.png|thumb]]

大多倫多地區與由[[加拿大統計局|加拿大統計局]]界定的多倫多人口普查都會區（Toronto Census Metropolitan Area）有所重疊，但部分在大多倫多地區覆蓋範圍内的城鎮則不被歸入普查區之内，兩者的定義因此並不一致。據2006年人口普查所示，普查區的面積有5,904平方公里，人口則有5,113,149人<ref name=CMA>{{cite web| url=http://www12.statcan.ca/english/census06/data/popdwell/Table.cfm?T=201&S=3&O=D&RPP=150| title=Population and dwelling counts, for census metropolitan areas and census agglomerations, 2006 and 2001 censuses - 100% data| date=2007-03-13| work=[[Statistics_Canada|Statistics Canada]], 2006 Census of Population| language=en| accessdate=2007-03-13| archive-date=2008-02-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080221141044/http://www12.statcan.ca/english/census06/data/popdwell/Table.cfm?T=201&S=3&O=D&RPP=150| dead-url=yes}}</ref>，兩項數據皆較大多倫多地區為少。[[奧沙華|奧沙華]]和{{le|布靈頓|Burlington, Ontario}}皆屬大多倫多地區，但前者構成一個獨立的普查區，而後者則屬咸美頓普查區。<ref name=CHASS>{{cite web|title=What's the difference between the Greater Toronto Area (GTA) and CMA Toronto (census metropolitan area)?|url=http://www.chass.utoronto.ca/datalib/caq/g1.htm|publisher=Computing in the Humanities and Social Sciences University of Toronto|language=en|accessdate=2010-03-02|archive-date=2010-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100409123126/http://www.chass.utoronto.ca/datalib/caq/g1.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>其他多倫多普查區内的城鎮（如[[錫姆科縣|錫姆科縣]]的{{le|新特坎瑟斯|New Tecumseth, Ontario}}和[[達弗林縣|德芙靈縣]]的{{le|芒挪鄉|Mono, Ontario}}）則不屬大多倫多地區。

